comment.narrative:
Pandemic has highly affected children of Devadasi families emotionally and mentally resulting in need for psychosocial support. As schools being closed, prevented them from access to learning and interactions. In order to address the above and to ensure children are protected, our project intervened with the following tools to Kishori clubs :
Science kits containing low cost materials covering 200+ experiments and modules. Apart from academic learning, these tools also help them to get engaged for better mental health status. 
Sports items to help children engage, participate, develop self-esteem, grow emotionally / physically. This was decided based on the recommendation of the Professional Counsellor after having a series of online sessions.;
